net.jqwik.api.arbitraries

Interface NullableArbitrary<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Arbitrary<T>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    BigDecimalArbitrary, BigIntegerArbitrary, ByteArbitrary, CharacterArbitrary, DoubleArbitrary, FloatArbitrary, IntegerArbitrary, LongArbitrary, ShortArbitrary, SizableArbitrary<U>, StringArbitrary

    public interface NullableArbitrary<T>
extends Arbitrary<T>
    Fluent interface to configure arbitraries that can generate null values. While Arbitrary.injectNull() works with any arbitrary, NullableArbitrary subtypes can be constraint using getTargetClass()
